<br>
&quot;Athelfi, today we coronate my daughter Acacia as Princess of Lykastia, and heir to my throne. Tali, Vera, Cayla, and Meslina go to the New One's hut. Bring her here, The Ceremony is to begin.&quot;<br>
<br>
Tali, Vera, Cayla, and Meslina walk to Acacia's Hut and enter. Cayla smiles as she takes Acacia's hand to lead her.<br>
<br>
&lt;Cayla&gt; &quot;Come, child, your are to be our New Princess. Let all the Amazon Nation rejoice on this day.&quot;<br>
<br>
Cayla and the others lead young Acacia to the Platform and walk her up the stairs and stand her beside Gabrielle.<br>
<br>
§Gabrielle§<br>
~Amazon Queen of Lykastia~<br>
&quot;Peace is worth fighting for!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#a62a2a><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uiiacaciaii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>IIAcaciaII</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#660000>(3/11/02 11:57 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Coronation of Princess Acacia</span><hr size=1> ::Acacia walked from her hut with the 5 Amazon  sent to get her she was dressed in her Amazon leathers she made her way to the platform her hair in a brade the young girl stood beside her mother proudly:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#DEB887><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugabrielleofthechakram.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gabrielle of the Chakram</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 59<br> <font color=#660000>(3/12/02 12:53 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ~The Ceremony~</span><hr size=1> The Amazons cheered as Acacia made her appearance. The quietened as Gabrielle raised a hand for silence she brought her arm back down and clasped it with the other behind her back.<br>
<br>
&quot;A queen is a chalice. Let us fill you with visions of our history, fragments of a time before we were Amazons,<br>
when cannibals slaughtered our men, and warriors like the great Samsara called on the shaman for a savior from the future, an Atmah . . . the first Cyane.&quot;<br>
<br>
She then reached into a small pouch and pulled out a amulet (necklace) and placed it around Acacia's neck.<br>
<br>
<br>
&quot;Tonight your coronation continues a ritual passed<br>
down to us through the ages. A ritual of music and movement, a celebration of community and joy, for we are a family, united in sisterhood. We are the creators and our own creations, The words and the music, both singer and song. Our traditions stretch back to the great Gaia herself, mother of us all, a tradition of dance-- of music-- of sacrifice-- of blood.&quot;<br>
<br>
Gabrielle was not one for blood in a ceremony she had changed that law.  As the Amazon drumers began beating slowly on their instruments, Gabby took a silver chalice from another Amazons hand and filled it with wine.  A bear cub walked up and sat next to Gabrielle's leg, it was Lykatian, the bear Artemis had given Gabby. Bears were the symbol of Lykastia. She handed the chalice of wine to Acacia.<br>
<br>
<br>
&quot;This wine symbolizes the blood we once used. The blood of our athelfi that have fallen before us. Drink it as a symbol of your honor and loyalty to your sisters. To your tribe.&quot; <br>
<br>
Gabrielle waited for Acacia to drink the wine.<br>
<br>
§Gabrielle§<br>
~Amazon Queen of Lykastia~<br>
&quot;Peace is worth fighting for!&quot;<br>
<br>
