<br>
&quot;Amazons!, Tonight we celebrate in honor of our new Princess...&quot;<br>
<br>
She hands an Amazon Crested Dagger to Acacia, it had her name engraved on it, and the hilt was in the shape of a fox. Then, a bear who was not Gabby's bear walked up to Acacia, he was wearing a collar with a small tag on it saying *To the New Princess, A bear named Sage*<br>
<br>
Gabby keeps her sword raised to the sky and shouts,<br>
<br>
&quot;ACACIA!!&quot;<br>
<br>
The Amazon cheer and holler as the Celebration begins many Amazons begin dancing around the fire, while others chat and eat listening to the drums with the soft beat. Gabrielle climbed down from the platform and took Acacia's hand leading her to the dancing by the fire. Gabby began dancing wildy as every Amazon did. The glare of the fire danced happily on everyones face for tonight was one of joy.<br>
<br>
It was Finished Acacia was Amazon Princess of Lykastia.<br>
<br>
§Gabrielle§<br>
~Amazon Queen of Lykastia~<br>
&quot;Peace is with fighting for!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#a62a2a><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ukayceryder.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kayce Ryder</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#660000>(3/22/02 8:16 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/variaavande/images/js1s.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~End of Coronation~</span><hr size=1> Kayce didn't dance. She sucked at it. But she sat by the fire and smiled at the new Princess. &quot;Congratulations,&quot; she said when Acacia looked her way. <p><html> <center> <font face="lucida blackletter" size="+1"> ~ Kayce Cyane Ryder ~ </font> </center> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#DEB887><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/usapphirearsenic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sapphire Arsenic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#660000>(3/22/02 8:18 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/variaavande/images/sapphiresm.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~End of Coronation~</span><hr size=1> Saph danced like a wild woman, screaming and yelling and doing all kinds of shyt. She even grabbed the Princess and danced a bit with her, then let go of her and continued in her insane ramblings. <p><html> <center> <font face="old english" size="+1" color="blue"> &#8224; Reality Fades With But One Kiss... &#8224; </font> </center> </html></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=